        "text": "# 5th Principle\nAlways think in terms of waves, sinusoids, fractals, power-laws, and rhythms or oscillations. Our friends Fourier and Heisenberg are still just around the corner. For understanding the human mind, calculus, the math of change and movement, has a priority above statistics.\n"
